subarr-subgen
=============

This repository builds on McCloudS/subgen by applying a small series of
patches required by the subarr orchestrator (https://github.com/coaxk/subarr).

Upstream project
----------------

  Project:  McCloudS/subgen
  URL:      https://github.com/McCloudS/subgen
  License:  See upstream LICENSE in the submodule at `upstream/` or visit
            https://github.com/McCloudS/subgen/blob/main/LICENSE

Upstream subgen does the heavy lifting — wrapping faster-whisper, exposing
the FastAPI service, handling subtitle output. Everything in this repository
modifies, extends, or builds around that upstream code.

What this repository adds
-------------------------

  - patches/         — discrete .patch files we apply on top of upstream
  - scripts/         — build, apply-patches, rebase-test tooling
  - docker/          — Dockerfile that pulls upstream + applies our patches
  - tests/           — unit and smoke tests for our patches specifically
  - .github/         — CI workflows (PR validation, release builds, weekly
                       rebase-test against upstream main)
  - docs/            — patch authoring guide, tagging scheme, upstream-sync
                       process

Distribution
------------

The published docker image (`ghcr.io/coaxk/subarr-subgen`) is a derived work
combining upstream subgen + our patches, distributed per upstream's license
terms. We do not redistribute upstream source code in this repository — the
submodule pulls it directly from McCloudS/subgen at build time.

